/BoxE { stroke [] 0 setdash exch hpt sub exch vpt add M
  0 vpt2 neg V hpt2 0 V 0 vpt2 V
  hpt2 neg 0 V closepath stroke } def
/TriUE { stroke [] 0 setdash vpt 1.12 mul add M
